gw.plugin.notification

Interface INotificationPlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin, java.rmi.Remote

    public interface INotificationPlugin
extends com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin
    This plugin is used to calculate Notification dates for a variety of purposes (e.g., Renewal, Cancellation, etc.)

    • Method Detail

      • getMaximumLeadTime

        int getMaximumLeadTime(java.util.Date effDate,
                       java.util.Map<PolicyLinePattern,Jurisdiction[]> lineToJurisdictions,
                       NotificationActionType actionType)
                throws java.rmi.RemoteException
        Finds the maximum value for the lead time column for all combinations of line of business and jurisdiction for the passed actionType and effDate. This value represents a lead time in days.
        Parameters:
        effDate - The effective date to use for this notification configuration lookup
        lineToJurisdictions - A map from line of business to array of jurisdictions for each line of business to use for this notification configuration lookup
        actionType - The action type to use for this notification configuration lookup
        Returns:
        The maximum value for the lead time column (in days)
        Throws:
        java.rmi.RemoteException - If any of the following are true:
        • lineToJurisdictions is empty
        • any jurisdiction array for any line of business is empty
        • any line of business or jurisdiction is null
        • actionType is null
        • any combination of line of business and jurisdiction has no matching notification configurations for the passed actionType on the passed effDate
